data.title: No wedding bells planned

data.text:
Jamie Lynn Spears and her baby’s 19-year-old daddy, Casey Aldridge, “don’t need to make the same mistake twice” and get hitched just because they’re pregnant, Aldridge’s uncle, Odus Jackson, told People.com. “They may or may not (get married),” he said. “But if they’re not in love and it was just a fantasy, they don’t need to make the same mistake twice.” Britney Spears’ 16-year-old sister announced to OK! magazine earlier this week that she’s three months pregnant with Aldridge’s baby.

Originally Published: December 21, 2007 at 12:00 a.m.
